          ],
          "workingSteps": [
            "$3 \\times \\dfrac{3}{4} = \\dfrac{9}{4} = 2\\dfrac{1}{4}$ kg"
          ]
        },
        {
          "label": "b",
          "questionText": "Flour costs $\\$2.40$ per kg.\nWork out the cost of $\\dfrac{3}{4}$ kg.",
